Package atmbranchfinderspring.resourceserver.annotations

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AccessTokenAuthenticated
    AccessTokenAuthenticated is an annotation that can be used on (Rest)Controller methods that need to be authenticated using "Authorization-code" grant type access tokens.
    AdminBasicAuthenticated
    AdminBasicAuthenticated is an annotation that can be used on (Rest)Controller methods that need to be authenticated by Basic Authentication just for admins.
    RequestTokenAuthenticated
    RequestTokenAuthenticated is an annotation that can be used on (Rest)Controller methods that need to be authenticated using "Client-Credentials" grant type access tokens.
    TPPBasicAuthenticated
    TPPBasicAuthenticated is an annotation that can be used on (Rest)Controller methods that need to be authenticated by Basic Authentication just for Third Party Providers.
